title: 10/19 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC); Best Stashes
description:
Is Andrew Luck droppable (4:15)? And could you dare consider dropping T.Y. Hilton? ... Best stash candidates to put on your bench (12:40). Sterling Shepard and Marvin Jones could be available, and we have some players who are widely available and should be stashed. We've also got the latest news for you (20:30) before we cover the tough calls like Dion Lewis, Joe Mixon, Keenan Allen, TEN RBs and more ... ATL-NE (25:50), CIN-PIT (34:41), DEN-LAC (40:20), NYJ-MIA (47:32), TB-BUF (52:45), TEN-CLE (1:00:15) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
